--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 36e87a4f269af074e86ec25091a07134, type: 3}
  m_Name: AC2_Return_Warm
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: The kind version is this. The world is always talking. Most people are simply too loud to hear it back.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: And you hear it?
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: Enough of it. Roots under the pavement. Heat moving through empty buildings. The little habits of places that would rather stay hidden.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: Once you listen long enough, you stop mistaking strangeness for chaos.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: That is very wise for someone running a second-hand shop.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: Books are only one of the things I collect.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Then help me with something practical. I have never seen frogs that enormous, and one of them was blocking your door outside.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: My door?
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Your door. Giant frog. Serious posture. No interest in negotiation.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: Oh no.
  - Speaker: Anticar
    Text: That was Gilbert. He is not supposed to leave the frontage unattended.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Go after him. I will watch the place.
    nextDialogue: {fileID: 0}
    statEffect:
      creativity: 0
      empathy: 1
      plantCorruption: 0
    relationshipEffect:
      npcId: anticar
      amount: 2
    extraEffects:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: d2d58ca231f34ba6a7abf21fe4e97502, type: 2}
  - choiceText: You keep saying that like Gilbert is a coworker.
    nextDialogue: {fileID: 0}
    statEffect:
      creativity: 0
      empathy: 1
      plantCorruption: 0
    relationshipEffect:
      npcId: anticar
      amount: 1
    extraEffects:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: d2d58ca231f34ba6a7abf21fe4e97502, type: 2}
  - choiceText: Please tell me the giant frog is the strangest thing here.
    nextDialogue: {fileID: 0}
    statEffect:
      creativity: 1
      empathy: 0
      plantCorruption: 0
    relationshipEffect:
      npcId: anticar
      amount: 0
    extraEffects:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: d2d58ca231f34ba6a7abf21fe4e97502, type: 2}
